&lt;li&gt;For blowing systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Completely oil free&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Can be used for vacuum (-100kPa) (-14.5psi)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

